<div class=Section1>

<h2>The height of the tropopause</h2>

<table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=638 style='width:478.5pt;
 mso-cellspacing:0in;mso-padding-alt:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt'>
